FuncDef: This command specifies the precedence of the SDP binding when there are multiple SDP bindings attached to one service endpoint. The value of zero can only be assigned to one SDP bind making it the primary SDP bind. When an SDP binding goes down, the next highest precedence SDP binding will begin to forward traffic.

ParaDef.Info: Specifies the spoke SDP precedence. Values-1 to 4.
Assigns primary precedence to this spoke SDP.
